# Remotion Prompt Studio — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete web application that lets you generate Remotion videos by typing prompts in a UI. Your Antigravity IDE agent picks up the prompt and generates all the video assets (script, voiceover, images, composition code), then the video renders and plays back in the UI.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["🖥️ Web UI<br/>localhost:5173"] -->|POST /api/prompt| B["⚙️ Express Server<br/>localhost:3001"]
    B -->|Writes .json| C["📁 .prompts/"]
    D["🧠 Antigravity IDE"] -->|Reads prompt| C
    D -->|Generates assets| E["📂 public/content/"]
    D -->|Writes .done| C
    B -->|Detects .done| F["📡 WebSocket"]
    F -->|Status update| A
    E -->|Serves video| A
```

