## How to Use

### Start the studio
```bash
cd c:\Users\ADMIN\Desktop\remotion
npm run start    # Starts both Express server + Vite UI
```

### Generate a video
1. Open **http://localhost:5173** in your browser
2. Select a template (News Short, Documentary, AI Summary, Custom)
3. Type your video prompt
4. Click **🚀 Generate Video**

### Two ways Antigravity processes your prompt

**Option A — Automated (file watcher):**
- Open this project in Antigravity IDE
- The agent will detect new `.prompts/*.json` files
- Follow the `prompt-watcher` skill workflow

**Option B — Manual (clipboard):**
- Click **📋 Copy Prompt** on any job
- Paste the clipboard text into Antigravity's chat
- The agent will generate the assets

### After the agent finishes
- Agent writes `.prompts/{id}.done` → UI auto-updates via WebSocket
- Rendered video plays in the center player
- Click **⬇ Download** to save the MP4
